Math-Int2Base
=============

Math::Int2Base - Perl extension for converting decimal
(base-10) integers into another number base from base-2 to
base-62, and back to decimal.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None (except Math::BigInt for tests).

